snippet.title: Game & Watch - Pinball (c)1983 Nintendo [MAME emulation footage]
snippet.description:
This is Nintendo's Game & Watch : Pinball running in MAME, it will be supported in 0.219.  Emulation by Algestam, unit purchased by Ryan Holtz.  Artwork this time around is from DarthMarino as hydef appears to be taking a well earned break.  With this emulated all official Dual Screen Game & Watch titles are now emulated, and only a handful of others remain.

Artwork link : https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1vl9O-0jIGCHHY_lrWpOwBtqTXEKsVGOY?usp=sharing
